#define R(p,a,t) mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(t))+sin(t)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h) (cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, in vec2 C)
{
    O=vec4(0);
	vec3 p,r=iResolution,
    d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1));
    float i=0.,g=0.,e,s,a,b;
	for(;i++<90.;){
        p=d*g;
        p.z-=.5;
        p=R(p,vec3(.577),iTime*.4);
        p-=i/2e4; //https://twitter.com/zozuar/status/1527091919511248897
        e=s=a=1.5;
        for(int i=0;i++<6;)
            p=.8-abs(p-.2),
            b=(length(p-clamp(p,-.1,.1))-.03)/s,
            e<b?a=b:a,
            e=min(e,b),
            s*=1.5,
            p*=1.5;
        g+=e;
        O+=.015/exp(i*i*e);
    }
    O.rgb*=mix(vec3(1),H(a*3.),.6);
    O*=O;    

}
